 <!-- HERO -->
   <section class="bg-[linear-gradient(120deg,rgba(2,6,23,.92),rgba(15,23,42,.85)),url(&#39;https://legalx24.com/img/drt-hero.jpg&#39;)] bg-cover bg-center text-white text-center px-5 py-[120px]"> 
      <h1 class="text-[clamp(36px,4.2vw,52px)] font-black"> DRT &amp; SARFAESI Act – Bank &amp; Financial Recovery Law </h1> 
      <p class="max-w-[950px] mx-auto mt-4 text-[17.5px] leading-[1.85]"> Debt Recovery Tribunal (DRT) and the SARFAESI Act are specialized legal mechanisms that empower banks and financial institutions to recover outstanding dues efficiently while maintaining fairness, transparency, and financial discipline. </p> </section> 
   <section class="bg-white px-5 py-[60px]"> 
      <div class="container mx-auto">
         <h2 class="text-[clamp(26px,3vw,36px)] font-extrabold text-slate-950 mb-3 after:content-[&#39;&#39;] after:block after:w-[70px] after:h-1 after:bg-violet-600 after:mt-2"> Introduction to DRT &amp; SARFAESI Laws </h2>
       <p class="text-[16px] text-slate-600 leading-[1.9] mb-3"> The Indian banking system relies on structured recovery laws to address loan defaults and non-performing assets. DRT and the SARFAESI Act together form the backbone of institutional loan recovery, reducing dependence on lengthy civil litigation. </p>
         <p class="text-slate-600 leading-[1.9]"> These laws are designed to protect public money, strengthen lender confidence, and ensure timely enforcement of repayment obligations while safeguarding borrower rights. </p>
      </div> </section> 
   <section class="bg-slate-50 px-5 py-[60px]"> 
      <div class="container mx-auto">
         <h2 class="text-[clamp(26px,3vw,36px)] font-extrabold text-slate-950 mb-3 after:content-[&#39;&#39;] after:block after:w-[70px] after:h-1 after:bg-violet-600 after:mt-2"> Debt Recovery Tribunal (DRT) </h2>
         <p class="text-slate-600 leading-[1.9] mb-3"> The Debt Recovery Tribunal is a specialized adjudicatory body established to adjudicate recovery cases filed by banks and financial institutions. It provides a faster and more focused forum compared to traditional courts. </p>
         <p class="text-slate-600 leading-[1.9] mb-4"> Proceedings before the Tribunal are summary in nature, allowing swift adjudication and issuance of recovery certificates for enforcement of dues. </p>
         <div class="bg-white border-l-[6px] border-violet-600 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg font-semibold"> DRT ensures speedy recovery of large financial debts while providing borrowers an opportunity to raise lawful objections. </div>
      </div> </section> 
   <section class="bg-white px-5 py-[60px]"> 
      <div class="container mx-auto">
         <h2 class="text-[clamp(26px,3vw,36px)] font-extrabold text-slate-950 mb-3 after:content-[&#39;&#39;] after:block after:w-[70px] after:h-1 after:bg-violet-600 after:mt-2"> SARFAESI Act – Enforcement of Secured Assets </h2>
         <p class="text-slate-600 leading-[1.9] mb-3"> The SARFAESI Act, 2002 empowers secured creditors to enforce security interests without prior court intervention. It allows lenders to take possession of secured assets and recover dues through lawful measures. </p>
         <p class="text-slate-600 leading-[1.9]"> The Act plays a crucial role in preventing asset deterioration and minimizing recovery delays in secured loan defaults. </p>
      </div> </section> 
   <section class="bg-white px-5 py-[60px]"> 
      <div class="container mx-auto">
         <div class="row items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
               <h2 class="text-[clamp(26px,3vw,36px)] font-extrabold text-slate-950 mb-3 after:content-[&#39;&#39;] after:block after:w-[70px] after:h-1 after:bg-violet-600 after:mt-2"> SARFAESI Recovery Procedure </h2>
               <p class="text-slate-600 leading-[1.9] mb-3"> The SARFAESI process begins with issuance of a statutory demand notice to the borrower demanding repayment of outstanding dues within the prescribed period. </p>
               <p class="text-slate-600 leading-[1.9] mb-3"> Upon failure to comply, the lender may take possession of the secured assets, appoint managers, or initiate sale proceedings strictly in accordance with law. </p>
               <p class="text-slate-600 leading-[1.9]"> Borrowers have the right to challenge such actions before the appropriate legal forum. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6"> 
               <img src="https://legalx24.com/img/sarfaesi-1.jpg" class="w-full rounded-[14px] shadow-xl" alt="SARFAESI Asset Recovery Process" data-themekey="#"/> &#160;</div>
         </div>
      </div> </section> 
   <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#020617] to-[#0f172a] text-white px-5 py-[60px]"> 
      <div class="container mx-auto">
         <h2 class="text-[clamp(26px,3vw,36px)] font-extrabold mb-3 after:content-[&#39;&#39;] after:block after:w-[70px] after:h-1 after:bg-violet-600 after:mt-2"> Relationship Between DRT and SARFAESI Act </h2>
         <p class="leading-[1.9] mb-3"> DRT and SARFAESI function as complementary mechanisms. While SARFAESI empowers lenders to take direct enforcement action, DRT provides judicial oversight and dispute resolution. </p>
         <p class="leading-[1.9]"> This dual framework ensures balance between efficient recovery and protection against arbitrary exercise of power. </p>
      </div> </section> 
   <section class="bg-white px-5 py-[60px]"> 
      <div class="container mx-auto">
         <h2 class="text-[clamp(26px,3vw,36px)] font-extrabold text-slate-950 mb-3 after:content-[&#39;&#39;] after:block after:w-[70px] after:h-1 after:bg-violet-600 after:mt-2"> Rights &amp; Remedies of Borrowers </h2>
         <p class="text-slate-600 leading-[1.9] mb-3"> Borrowers are entitled to statutory notices, fair opportunity to respond, and legal remedies against non-compliant recovery actions. </p>
         <p class="text-slate-600 leading-[1.9]"> The law ensures transparency and accountability in recovery proceedings, preventing misuse of recovery powers. </p>
      </div> </section> 
   <section class="bg-slate-50 px-5 py-[60px]"> 
      <div class="container mx-auto">
         <h2 class="text-[clamp(26px,3vw,36px)] font-extrabold text-slate-950 mb-3 after:content-[&#39;&#39;] after:block after:w-[70px] after:h-1 after:bg-violet-600 after:mt-2"> Importance of Legal Strategy in DRT &amp; SARFAESI Matters </h2>
         <p class="text-slate-600 leading-[1.9] mb-3"> Recovery proceedings under DRT and SARFAESI involve strict timelines, financial documentation, and procedural compliance. </p>
         <p class="text-slate-600 leading-[1.9]"> Professional legal guidance ensures lawful enforcement, faster recovery, and effective representation for banks, institutions, and borrowers. </p>
      </div> </section> 
